{"tid":370870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［First Kill] 男子九龍城碼頭墮海亡","createTime":"2017-08-23T09:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T09:37:01.000Z","uid":7355,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"162a9baf6c8d41c85bdfd8aa9cab6f9bba9ef6b5","tid":370870,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:35:43.000Z","msg":"颱風「天鴿」來襲，為本港帶來狂風暴雨，下午3時許，本港仍然懸掛8號風球期間，有途人發現1名男子在九龍城碼頭對開墮海，載浮載沉，附近船員見狀立即跳落水拯救但不成功，遂即通知消防到場協助。<br />\n<br />\n消防到場後將墮海男子救起，然後送往附近公眾碼頭上岸，再由救護車將他送院，可惜經搶救後不治，警方正調查事件原因<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170823&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57118059 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170823%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57118059%20&d=dMw%2FSDUuvxnscJWfGjG4dwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=9786e197\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170823%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57118059%20&h=a2773089\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170823&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57118059 </a>"},{"pid":"dbcbcce1b6ff5545d6ebc587fff79dcf56a50e9a","tid":370870,"uid":83998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:37:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>颱風「天鴿」來襲，為本港帶來狂風暴雨，下午3時許，本港仍然懸掛8號風球期間，有途人發現1名男子在九龍城碼頭對開墮海，載浮載沉，<span style=\"color: red;\">附近船員見狀立即跳落水拯救</span>但不成功，遂即通知消防到場協助。<br />\n<br />\n消防到場後將墮海男子救起，然後送往附近公眾碼頭上岸，再由救護車將他送院，可惜經搶救後不治，警方正調查事件原因<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170823&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57118059 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170823%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57118059%20&d=dMw%2FSDUuvxnscJWfGjG4dwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=9786e197\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170823%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57118059%20&h=a2773089\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170823&amp;s=10829391